Class SearchIntensification<V extends Variable<V,T>,T extends Value<V,T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.extension.Extension<V,T>
      • org.cpsolver.ifs.assignment.context.ExtensionWithContext<V,T,SearchIntensification.Context>
        • org.cpsolver.ifs.extension.SearchIntensification<V,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - Variable
    T - Value
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    CanHoldContext, HasAssignmentContext<V,T,SearchIntensification.Context>, ModelListener<V,T>, SolutionListener<V,T>

    public class SearchIntensification<V extends Variable<V,T>,T extends Value<V,T>>
extends ExtensionWithContext<V,T,SearchIntensification.Context>
implements SolutionListener<V,T>
    Go back to the best known solution when no better solution is found within the given amount of iterations.
    Version:
    IFS 1.3 (Iterative Forward Search)
